<TEXT>
<P>
 Europa, Europa (Bravo Sunday at 5 and 11:30 p.m.; Friday at 6 and 11 p.m.) is 
Agnieszka Holland's superb intimate epic about a Polish-Jewish refugee who 
hides his identity only to wind up drafted into the German army. 
