<P>
TV Times; Page 6; Television Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
35 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
TALKING HEADS WITH BODIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The TV Times cover (July 24) on "Teen Hunks" reads "They're cute.They're nice. 
They like to work out, smile and sneer." This could be used to describe the 
city's news anchors. 
</P>
<P>
 Jane Cowans, Los Angeles 
</P>
