<HEADLINE>
<P>
RECORD RACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Dennis Hunt 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *** Ahmad, "Ahmad," Giant. At 18, this South-Central rapper may seem a bit 
young for nostalgia pangs, but his hit single "Back in the Day" -- a yearning 
for a simpler times -- is still very convincing.It's the best song on the 
gangsta-flavored rookie effort by this nimble-tongued rhyming whiz. Mostly 
upbeat, always insightful and sometimes very funny. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent).  
</P>
<P>
 Dennis Hunt 
</P>
