</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Randy Lewis 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 ** Diamond Rio, "Love a Little Stronger," Arista. What's the difference 
between Diamond Rio and the Cowardly Lion? The Cowardly Lion knew his heart was 
missing.The most interesting cut is "Appalachian Dream," a scenically winding 
instrumental. When it comes to songs with lyrics, any glimmers of honest 
expression are quickly extinguished by the surrounding emotional vacuum. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent).  
</P>
<P>
 Randy Lewis 
</P>
