 Regarding your Film Clip on the movie "To Wong Foo, Thanks for Everything, 
Julie Newmar" (July 17): How dare you relegate her to the status of "B-movie 
actress." For my money (which there isn't much of), Newmar is the definitive 
Catwoman, featured on the "Batman" TV series. 
