<TEXT>
<P>
 David L. Cargile has been appointed president and chief operating officer of 
US Facilities Corp. in Costa Mesa.Cargile had been senior vice president of the 
company since 1991. 
</P>
<P>
 The previous president, George Kadonada, remains as the company's chief 
executive and chairman of its board. The chief operating officer's role is 
newly created, said a company spokeswoman. 
</P>
<P>
