<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH: SOUTH-CENTRAL; HOUSING, CONSUMER FAIR ON SATURDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Community Financial Resource Center will host a Housing and Consumer Fair 
on Saturday to introduce products and services of financial institutions and 
community organizations. 
</P>
<P>
 The fair is from 8:30 a.m. to 3 p.m. at the Crenshaw Christian Center, 7901 S. 
Vermont Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 Banks, community organizations and resource center staff will address 
homeowner fraud prevention, refinancing, low-income home-buyer programs, 
consumer credit and debt management and earthquake-damage assistance. A 
Spanish-language home buyer workshop will also be offered. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 233-1900. 
</P>
</TEXT>
