COMMUNITY NEWS: MID-CITY: MID-CITY AREA; CHAMBER MIXER IS ON A ROLL -- AND BOWL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Mid-City Chamber of Commerce is inviting area merchants and community 
groups to join in a bowling-and-skating business and community mixer Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Participants will be allowed to set up display tables, as well as skate and 
bowl for prizes.  
</P>
<P>
 The event starts at 6:30 p.m. at Midtown Bowling Center & World on Wheels, 
4645 Venice Blvd. Admission is $6 with proceeds going to the chamber. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 933-7171. 
