<P>
AMATEUR BOUTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Bassett Boxing Club will hold amateur bouts today at Bassett Park, 510 N. 
Vineland, City of Industry. Weigh-ins begin at 10 a.m. Amateur shows will also 
be held Saturday at 1 p.m. at Lynwood Activities League, 3100 E. Imperial Ave., 
Lynwood, and Sunday at 1 p.m. at the Toberman Settlement House, 131 N. Grand 
Ave., San Pedro. Weigh-ins begin at 9 a.m. for both contests. 
</P>
